Welcome to the InterActive Digital Devices PC Pedals(TM) information directory.
This Directory contains a text file providing  a detailed description of the
PC PEDALS(TM), a text file with ordering and pricing information, and several
IFF drawings showing multiple views and close-ups of the PC PEDALS(TM).
You will also find a several example of wiring hookups int the seperate
directory called "Connection Diagrams"

This Directory should contain the following files:
 1: Description   --- A detailed description of the PC PEDALS(TM)
 2: Order Info    --- Ordering information for ALL of IDD's products
 3: PC PEDALS     --- IFF picture: Overall view from the right side
 4: PC PEDALS1    --- IFF picture: Overall view from the Left side
 5: PEDALS Conn.  --- IFF picture: Close-up of left side showing connectors
 6: PEDALS Left   --- IFF picture: Overall Close-up of left side
 7: PC Stick Shift--- IFF picture: Drawing of PC Stick Shift (Future product)
 8: ReadMe        --- This file

Thank you for considering InterActive Digital Devices products.

